name: Zootopia 768
description:
These are another batch of high quality SD model 2.X embeddings that I am excited to release to the stable diffusion community! My new Zootopia embedding delivers the magic Look of the Movie! Make imaginary movie scenes with a high degree of reliability and flexibility! To get sharp and Crisp Edges use the SD upscaler with SwinIR and denoising on .3

As with all other high quality embeddings, you can mix and match to create unique and interesting novel art styles! Check out @SoCalGuitarists GTA768, SDA768 and Inkpunk768 embeddings for more great styles on demand!

--------

To use these embeddings in AUTOMATIC1111, copy them to your embeddings folder in your stable-diffusion-webui directory. No need to restart, just invoke the embedding from your prompt. Make sure you are using a compatible model or you will get errors!

--------

Versions

Zootopiav4 - Gives You The Look of the Movie in all parts, animals now have big eyes and are fluffy, get creative with your prompts and really try a lot of tags to get the image to your liking

💖💖I hope you enjoy using these embeddings in your art as much as I enjoy creating them for the Stable Diffusion community. 🙏🏼🙏🏼If you do like them, can you pretty please click the heart at the top and leave a review? Many thanks! 💖💖
